mporary thought about the volume.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 7aHISTORY / Native American.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520342354?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520342354423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520342354/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles